# Title: Invoke-Obfuscation VAR+ Launcher - Security
# Author: Jonathan Cheong, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-15
# Level: high
# Description: Detects Obfuscated use of Environment Variables to execute PowerShell
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.t1027, attack.execution, attack.t1059.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/security/win_security_invoke_obfuscation_var_services_security.yml

EventID=4697 ServiceFileName IN ("*/c*", "*/r*") ServiceFileName="*cmd*" ServiceFileName="*\"set*" ServiceFileName="*-f*"